annotationA: Probable 39S ribosomal protein L24, mitochondrial; Structural constituent of ribosome. It is involved in the biological process described with: translation; Belongs to the universal ribosomal protein uL24 family
annotationB: 40S ribosomal protein S18; Located at the top of the head of the 40S subunit, it contacts several helices of the 18S rRNA
